tafsir[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,"Allah woondirii keneeli jarotoo…ói leydi ndin !"
  51,2,"Mi woondirii kadi duule ronndotoo…óe to…ìo tii…óngo !"
  51,3,"Mi woondirii kadi laa…óe dogiray…óe ka maayo …óen no newori !"
  51,4,"E malaykaaji peccooji ko Alla yamiri yo fecce ko e fiyakuuji jiyaa…ìe."
  51,5,"Ko Alla fodata on ko e hasbeede e yo…ìeede ko goongo mbo alah jeddi."
  51,6,"Haasbeede ko ko wonat nyande darngo alah e sago."
  51,7,"Allah woondirii kammu labaangu tagu jom …óate ngun."
  51,8,"Pellet, onon yim…ìe Makka …ìee, hi…óon e konngol piyondirngol : nde wonnde wi'on : Alqur'aana ko mbilewu, nde wonnde kadi wi'on : ko nde gimi, ma wi'on kadi nde wonnde: Muhammadu ko mbileejo, e wonnde goo wi'on : ko yimoowo."
  51,9,"Hino yiltee e gom…óingol Alqur'aana e Annabiijo on (yo o his) kala firlitaa…óo e anndal Allah, e gom…óinal ngal; anndugol Mo wonnde on…óon gom…óintaa, ko …óum wa…ói si O firlitaa."
  51,10,"∆Åee fenu…ìe e hoore Alqur'aana e Annabiijo ma…ì…ìe on fow …ìe hu…óaama."
  51,11,"∆Åen yoolii…ìe e majjere, welsindii…ìe fii galle laakara …óen."
  51,12,"Hi…ìe lamndoo : ko honnde woni √ëalaande njo…ìdi kuu…óe? Hara non …ìe alaa gollannde nde !"
  51,13,"Allah jaaboo lamndal ma…ì…ìe ngal : ko √ëalaande nde …ìe leptoytee ka Yiite."
  51,14,"∆Åe wi'ane : mee…óee non lepte mon …óen ; ko …óum woni ko hawjirayno…óon kon, wa…óton jalnori, tuma jertinteno…óon."
  51,15,"Pellet …ìeen hulir…ìe Joomi mum en …óoftaade jamirooje Makka, e reenaade ka…óaa…óe Makka √±ande darngo ho…ìe e jardeeji e caalli dogooji."
  51,16,"Jaggatnoo…ìe ko Alla okkata…ìe e njo…ìdi teddundi, …ìe pellet ko adii ndii njo…ìdi ho…ìe mo∆¥∆¥inatno golle ka aduna."
  51,17,"Ho…ìe njuulatno jemma, …ìe …óaanatanooko si wonah setta."
  51,18,"E saanga ndoogu ho…ìe toro yaafeede bakkatuuji mum en ummorde ka Alla."
  51,19,"Ina e jawle mum en he hakke-ho…ìe ngattoo heen- yim…ìe √±aagatoo…ìe e …ìe √±aagataako,yim…ìe ha…óiraa…ìe arsuko e kala sabaabu."
  51,20,"E nder leydi ko Alla wa…ói ko e hendi ummaade e tule haa e maaje e caalli e le…ó…óe e pu…ói e kulle, ko dallillaaji mbaawko Alla wonande yananaa…ìe wonde ko Alla woni tak…óo mbaadin…óo."
  51,21,"Ina e nder pittaali mon - onon aade en- dallillaaji kollirooji mbaawko Alla, mbela on ndaaratah ngam teska …óon?"
  51,22,"Ina nder kammu arsuko mon aduna, ina e hembo ko podante …óon e mo∆¥∆¥e e bonannde."
  51,23,"Mi woondirii Jom kammu e leydi, pellet ummital ko goongo mbo alah sikke e mum, hono no sikke waasi wonde e haala mon saanga nde kaalaton."
  51,24,"Mbela arii e ma -Aan Nulaa…óo- yeewtere ho…ó…ìe Ibraahiima jeyaa…ìe e malaykaaji, …ìe Alla teddini."
  51,25,"Nde…ìe naati e makko, …ìe mbi*ni mbo salaaman: Ibraahiima rutti…ìe salminaandu, nduun woni salaam, O maaki e fittaandu makko: …ìe ko yim…ìe …ìe nganndaaka."
  51,26,"O fayi to yim…ìe makko e mbaadi cuuiindi, o addori toon ngaari payndi, sabu o sikkuno ko…ìe yim…ìe."
  51,27,"O …ìanni …ìe ngaari ndi, o haaldi e ma…ì…ìe e newuya: mbela on √±aamatah?"
  51,28,"Nede …ìe waasno √±aamde o so*i e fittaandu makko he kulol, …ìe paami …óuum, …ìe lelnir …ìernde makko wiide taa hulu, minen komin nulaa…ìe ummaade ka Alla, …ìe kabri mbo ko welata mbo, …óuum woni ma o he…ì keew…óo ganndal, ko oon woni Ishaaqa."
  51,29,"Nde jom suudu makko nani o wela wela o ari homo wulla ngam weltaare, o hellii yeeso makko, o wii hombo haawa: mbela nayeeja na jibina, te kanko ko o dimara."
  51,30,"Malaykaaji …ói mbi* imbo ko min kabru ma ko woni ko Joom ma daali, ko O daali ko noon ruttetaake, ko Kanko woni √±ee√±u…óo e tagu Makko e hoddiro Makko, ganndo tagu Makko e ko nafata…ìe."
  51,31,"Annabi Ibraahiima maaki Malaa'i…ìe …ìen : ko hon…óum woni fii mon? E ko faanditi…óon?"
  51,32,"Malaa'ika'en jaabii mo wonnde : menen, Allah neli men e yim…ìe bom…ìe …ìen faggitotoo…ìe kuu…óe bon…óe."
  51,33,"Fii yo men accitu e ma…ì…ìe, kaa∆¥e iw…óe e loope ju…óaa…óe"
  51,34,"Maandiniraa…óe ka Joomi maa an Ibraahiima, wurtaa…óe e yawtoo…ìe keeri Allah …ìen, fantinoo…ìe yeddugol Mo ngol."
  51,35,"Men yaltini taho kala gom…óim…ìe wonunoo…ìe e saare yim…ìe Luutu …ìen, fii wata lepte bom…ìe …ìen hawru e ma…ì…ìe."
  51,36,"Men tawaano e nden saare, si wanaa suudu juul…ìe wooturu, ndun le ko suudu …ìeynguure Luutu nden (yo o his)."
  51,37,"men acci e nden saare yim…ìe Luutu, batteeji lepte …óen, ko holla wonnde …óe yanuno e ma…ì…ìe, wona waajitor…óum kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen yanunoo…óe e ma…ì…ìe, ontigi hula wa…óugol sugu kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen, fii da…óugol …óen lepte."
  51,38,"Men acci kadi maande e Muusaa, tuma nde Men nulunoo mo e Fir'awna, wonndude e hujjaaji …ìanngu…ói, wonannde kala huloowo e lepte muusu…óe …óen."
  51,39,"Kono Fir'awna …óuurni fawaade e cemmbe e konu makko fow salii goonga, o wi'i Muusaa : ko mbil…óotoo…óo yim…ìe maa hara feetu…óo."
  51,40,"Men nanngi mo kanko e koneeli makko …óin fow, Men weddii …ìe ka maayo, …ìe yoolii …ìe halkii, tawde Fir'awna ko feliraa…óo fennugol mo ngol nodditoo rewetee…óo."
  51,41,"Men acci kadi maande e 'Adi'en, yim…ìe Huudu …ìen, wonannde kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen, tuma nde Men wurtunoo e ma…ì…ìe henndu ndu ardaa e to…ìo, ndu worgintaa le…ó…óe ndu aldaa kadi e barke."
  51,42,"Ndu accataa hay wonkii maa jawdi ekw e kon ko ndu arani, si wanaa ndu muncay fii mun, ndu wa…óta …óum wano rappunde sariinde."
  51,43,"Men wa…ói kadi maande e Samuuda'en, yim…ìe Annabi Saalih …ìen, wonannde kala huloowo lepte muusu…óe …óen, tuma nde …ìe wi'ananoo : awa dakmitoree nguurndam mon …óam, ado lajal mon gal timmude."
  51,44,"∆Åe townitanii yawmiroore Joomi ma…ì…ìe gom…óingol e …óoftagol Mo ngol, haacaango lepte ngon nanngi …ìe, tawi hi…ìe ∆¥eewa ko …óum jippotoo kon. Tawde …ìe kammbirano lepte …óen, bal…óe tati ado …óe jippaade."
  51,45,"∆Åe waawaano du√±ugol lepte …óen gaay e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe he…ìaano kadi feere faabeede."
  51,46,"Gom…óii kadi Men halkiriino yim…ìe Nuuhu …ìen ado …ìee jantaa…ìe …óoo, yoolagol. Pellet, …ìen ko yim…ìe yaltunoo…ìe e …óoftaare Allah, wa…ói si …ìe hanndi e lepte Makko …óen."
  51,47,"Kammu ngun, Men mahir ngu doole Amen, Men …óiggini …óum. Pellet, ko Men yaanoo…ìe cebe mammba."
  51,48,"Leydi ndin kan, Men weertiranndi ho…óoo…ìe …ìen, wano nda…ó…óundi ma…ì…ìe. Men mo∆¥∆¥ii weertan …ìe ndi."
  51,49,"E kala huunde, Men tagii noone …ói…ói: wano deyel e gorel, kammu e leydi, njodrndi e maayo; balajo'o on waajitoray gootaagu Allah tagu…óo …óin On, tesko…óon fii kattal Makko ngal."
  51,50,"Dogee lepte Allah …óen, yaccoron e mbarjaari Makko ndin, …óoftaare e anngal yeddugol Mo. Min, wonannde on onon …ìee yim…ìe, ko mi jertinoowo e lepte Makko …óen, …ìanngu…óo jertinol."
  51,51,"Wata on wa…óde e Allah rewetee…óo goo ko rewon. Min, wonannde on immorde ka Makko, ko mi …ìanngu…óo jertinol."
  51,52,"nKo wano yim…ìe Makko …ìen fenniri nii, mofte adinoo…ìe …ìen fennirnoo. Nulaa…óo Allah araali e …ìen, si wanaa …ìe wi'ay mo : ko mbileejo maa feetu…óo!"
  51,53,"Hara heefer…ìe adinoo…ìe …ìen yamondirno e sakkitii…ìe …ìen e ngol fennugol Nulaa…ìe? Oo'o woye. Ko woni kon, ko bewre renndini…ìe e mum."
  51,54,"An Nulaa…óo, selu …ìee fennoo…ìe, a wonaa felnii…óo. Ko pellet, a yottinii ko nula…óaa kon e ma…ì…ìe."
  51,55,"Ha…óataa si a selii …ìe, waajoraa …ìe anndintinaa …ìe; tawde waajagol anndina ngol, hino nafa gom…óim…ìe Allah …ìen."
  51,56,"Mi tagiraali jinna e yim…ìe, si wanaa fii yo …ìe rewan Min tun. Wanaa dey fii yo …ìe waddam e go…ó…óum goo."
  51,57,"Mi …óa…ì…ìiraa …ìe arsike; Mi …óa…ì…ìiraa …ìe yo …ìe √±amminam."
  51,58,"Pellet, ko Allah woni arsikoowo jeyaa…ìe …ìen, fow no hatonjini e arsike Makko On, Kanko Jom cemmbe tii…óu…óe …óe huunde foolataa. Denndangal jinna e yim…ìe ko cemmbe Makko …óen yankinanii."
  51,59,"Haray hino woodani too√±ir…ìe ko'e mun …ìen fennugol ma, an Nulaa…óo, ge…ìal e lepte, yeru ge…ìal nanndo ma…ì…ìe'en adinoo…ìe …ìen. ∆äum no happanaa lajal, wata …ìe …óa…ì…ìiram yaccinangol …ìe …óum ado happu mun on."
  51,60,"Halkaare woodanii …ìen yeddu…ìe Allah, …ìe fenni Nulaa…óo Makko on, e nden √ëalaande Darngal nde …ìe kammbiranaa yanugol lepte …óen e ma…ì…ìe."
